column5: My mouth is watering at the sight of that, but hamburgs are what is on my BBQ. Enjoy your dinner!

My mouth is watering at the sight of that, but hamburgs are what is on my BBQ. Enjoy your dinner!  Hambugers and sausage were cooking.Had skin on fried chips as well. Need a 4 hour work out on the toon now. LOL  Looks great
Prices are coming down now that the tourist season is over, they were $16.99 /lb a week ago.
